'''朝鲜－新加坡關係'''是指[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]和[[新加坡共和國|新加坡共和國]]的[[國際關係學|双边]]关系。

新加坡和朝鲜在1975年11月8日建立外交關係。<ref name="Consular and Diplomatic List">{{Cite web|url=http://app1.mfa.gov.sg/pdf/dipconopen.pdf|title=Consular and Diplomatic List|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=12 December 2014|publisher=Singapore Ministry of Foreign Affairs|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141128161304/http://app1.mfa.gov.sg/pdf/dipconopen.pdf|archivedate=2014年11月28日}}</ref>朝鲜在新加坡有派駐大使馆，而后者則是在[[北京|北京]]派駐非常大使負責對[[平壤|平壤]]的外交業務。当前朝鲜的驻新加坡大使是鄭松日（Jong Song Il）。<ref name="Consular and Diplomatic List">{{Cite web|url=http://app1.mfa.gov.sg/pdf/dipconopen.pdf|title=Consular and Diplomatic List|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=12 December 2014|publisher=Singapore Ministry of Foreign Affairs|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141128161304/http://app1.mfa.gov.sg/pdf/dipconopen.pdf|archivedate=2014年11月28日}}</ref>

新加坡曾有[[朝鲜绑架日本人问题|一名女子]]在1978年離奇失蹤，懷疑被朝鮮特工綁架至朝鮮。

朝鲜的公民進出新加坡享有免簽證服務。<ref name="Countries/Regions Requiring Visa">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ica.gov.sg/services_centre_overview.aspx?pageid=252&secid=165/www.ica.gov.sg/services_centre_overview.aspx?pageid=252&secid=165|title=Countries/Regions Requiring Visa|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=12 December 2014|publisher=MFA Singapore|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320113430/http://www.ica.gov.sg/services_centre_overview.aspx?pageid=252&secid=165%2Fwww.ica.gov.sg%2Fservices_centre_overview.aspx%3Fpageid%3D252&secid=165|archivedate=2015年3月20日}}</ref>新加坡公民若因商務或旅遊要進出北韓，持有普通护照並不超過30天亦无需签证。 <ref name="Visa Information">{{Cite web|url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?SpecData=1&VISA=&page=visa&NA=SG&AR=00&PASSTYPES=PASS&DE=KP&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C|title=Visa Information|accessdate=25 March 2015|date=25 March 2015|publisher=IATA}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>朝鲜人偶尔會前往新加坡就醫。<ref name="Is Kim Jong-un's Aunt Dead?">{{Cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/01/06/2014010600689.html|title=Is Kim Jong-un's Aunt Dead?|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=6 January 2014|publisher=Chosun Ilbo|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322141742/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/01/06/2014010600689.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 国际组织 ==
朝鲜和新加坡都是[[不结盟运动|不结盟运动]]的參與國，新加坡在1970年加入，朝鲜則在1976年加入。朝鲜民主主义人民共和国從2000年以來也參與[[东南亚国家联盟|東協区域论坛]]，新加坡為該論壇發起者東盟的創始成員國。<ref name="DPRK ASEAN">{{Cite web|url=http://nkleadershipwatch.wordpress.com/category/dprk-asean/page/2/|title=DPRK-ASEAN Archive|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=8 July 2014|publisher=NK Leadership Watch|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141212072130/http://nkleadershipwatch.wordpress.com/category/dprk-asean/page/2/|archivedate=2014年12月12日}}</ref>

== 正式访问 ==
朝鲜民主主义人民共和国正式访问新加坡時往往一同访问东南亚其他国家。2014年，外務相[[李洙墉|李洙墉]]访问了新加坡。<ref name="Foreign Minister Ri Su Yong's Southeast Asia Tour Roundup">{{Cite web|url=http://www.chosonexchange.org/our-blog/2014/8/14/foreign-minister-ri-su-yongs-southeast-asia-tour-roundup|title=Foreign Minister Ri Su Yong's Southeast Asia Tour Roundup|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=14 August 2014|publisher=Choson Exchange|archive-date=2019-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110131730/https://www.chosonexchange.org/our-blog/2014/8/14/foreign-minister-ri-su-yongs-southeast-asia-tour-roundup|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2012年[[最高人民会议|最高人民会议]]常任委員會委員長也访问了新加坡。<ref name="N Korea taking lessons from Singapore">{{Cite web|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/world/archives/2012/05/14/2003532798|title=N Korea taking lessons from Singapore|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=14 May 2012|publisher=Taipei Times|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613085705/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/world/archives/2012/05/14/2003532798|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他朝鲜精英亦曾訪問新加坡，如[[金正恩|金正恩]]的親戚[[金正男|金正男]]、[[金正哲|金正哲]]和[[张成泽|张成泽]]，其他政府要員也都訪問過新加坡，如[[朴南基|朴南基]]。<ref name="Kim Jong-nam Resurfaces in Singapore">{{Cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2012/11/15/2012111500557.html|title=Kim Jong-nam Resurfaces in Singapore|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=15 November 2012|publisher=Chosun Ilbo|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811224104/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2012/11/15/2012111500557.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="N.Korean Princeling 'Well Looked-After' in Singapore">{{Cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/02/17/2011021700813.html|title=N.Korean Princeling 'Well Looked-After' in Singapore|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=17 February 2011|publisher=Chosun Ilbo|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811223154/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/02/17/2011021700813.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

新加坡外交部长[[杨荣文|杨荣文]]曾在2008年访问朝鲜。<ref name="National Archives Press Release">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nas.gov.sg/archivesonline/speeches/record-details/7f80ff28-115d-11e3-83d5-0050568939ad|title=OFFICIAL VISIT BY MINISTER FOR FOREIGN AFFAIRS GEORGE YEO TO THE DEMOCRATIC PEOPLE'S REPUBLIC OF KOREA (DPRK) AND THE PEOPLE'S REPUBLIC OF CHINA (PRC): MINISTRY OF FOREIGN AFFAIRS PRESS STATEMENT|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=9 May 2008|publisher=Singapore National Archives|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024154259/http://www.nas.gov.sg/archivesonline/speeches/record-details/7f80ff28-115d-11e3-83d5-0050568939ad|dead-url=no}}</ref>外交部常务秘书Bilahari Kausikan也曾在2006年和2008年访问朝鲜。<ref name="Singapore Diplomats offer Readout on Recent Trip to Pyongyang">{{Cite web|url=https://cablegatesearch.wikileaks.org/cable.php?id=09SINGAPORE1239|title=Singapore Diplomats offer Readout on Recent Trip to Pyongyang|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=23 December 2009|publisher=Wikileaks|archive-date=2015-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902011550/https://cablegatesearch.wikileaks.org/cable.php?id=09SINGAPORE1239|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年6月10日，[[朝鮮勞動黨委員長|朝鮮勞動黨委員長]]、[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國國務委員會委員長|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國國務委員會委員長]][[金正恩|金正恩]]訪問新加坡并且出席[[2018年朝美首腦會議|朝美首腦會議]]。新加坡总理[[李显龙|李显龙]]于6月10日下午在[[新加坡總統府|新加坡總統府]]会见了金正恩。<ref>{{cite web |title=North Korean leader Kim Jong Un meets Prime Minister Lee Hsien Loong ahead of Trump-Kim summit |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/north-korean-leader-kim-jong-un-meets-prime-minister-lee-hsien-loong-ahead-of-trump-kim |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=10 June 2018 |date=10 June 2018 |archive-date=2018-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611144805/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/north-korean-leader-kim-jong-un-meets-prime-minister-lee-hsien-loong-ahead-of-trump-kim |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 经济培训 ==
朝鲜人經常組團访问新加坡，培训经济政策、创业精神和法律方面的相關人員。<ref name="N.Korean Officials Learn Capitalism in Singapore">{{Cite web|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/01/02/2014010201327.html|title=N.Korean Officials Learn Capitalism in Singapore|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=2 January 2014|publisher=Chosun Ilbo|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111220511/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/01/02/2014010201327.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>朝鲜政府認為，新加坡的经济发展和政治是非常稳定的。<ref name="Singapore Diplomats offer Readout on Recent Trip to Pyongyang">{{Cite web|url=https://cablegatesearch.wikileaks.org/cable.php?id=09SINGAPORE1239|title=Singapore Diplomats offer Readout on Recent Trip to Pyongyang|accessdate=12 December 2014|date=23 December 2009|publisher=Wikileaks}}</ref>

